
  <sn><md>### The Middle English Period {.text-center}

**Duration: 1066–1500**

There are three notable eras in this period:

* **(a) 1066–1340:** The Anglo-Norman Period
* **(b) 1340–1400:** The Age of Chaucer
* **(c) 1400–1485/1500:** The Dark / Barren Period
